nodes.text: Corey Vidal (born December 7, 1986) is a Canadian Star Wars video content producer, digital media consultant, and YouTube Partner. His YouTube videos have been seen over 71 million times, and his YouTube channel has been viewed over 9 million times. His most viewed video, "Star Wars (John Williams Is The Man) A Cappella Tribute," has over 19.9 million views. In December 2007, Corey was one of the first Canadians to join the YouTube Partnership Program.
Corey was also one of the hosts for the Star Wars Celebration Anaheim Live, along with Anthony Carboni and Andi Gutierrez.
